{
  "texts": [
    "While it offers great explanations, it appears difficult for a student or resident physician to learn from it if the rationale may be wrong approximately half the time.Other suggestions have been made for ChatGPT's educational applicability through use in small group settings [3,11].",
    "Due to its ability to provide human like dialogic responses, it could fill the role of a peer to enable individuals studying independently to ask for clarification on hard to understand medical concepts, diagnoses, or treatments [3].",
    "A meta-analysis on this form of teaching showed that peer learning is as efficacious as learning from faculty [3,21].",
    "Multiple studies have commented that the quality of ChatGPT's explanations are of high clarity and relevance with low levels of self-contradiction [5,8,19,22].",
    "Limitations of the studyA large percentage of cases reviewed by orthopedic surgeons require imaging in creating differential diagnoses."
  ]
}